replyContent: Hi Artemio, SignalCheck does not claim to increase your signal strength; no software application has the ability to do that. Many things factor into your signal strength, including your device's hardware, the distance and obstacles (walls/trees/mountains/etc) between your device and the cell site, and the configuration of the cell site's antennas.
